# FinancialIntelligence — Git Ignore
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SECURITY RULE: Never commit real financial data, statements, or API keys.
# The patterns below enforce this at the repository level.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Secrets & credentials ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
*.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
# Kubernetes Secret files — template is safe to commit; populated file is not
k8s/secret.yaml

# ── PDF statement files — NEVER commit real bank statements ──────────────────
# (catch-all regardless of location in the repo)
*.pdf
*.PDF
*.ofx
*.qfx
*.qbo

# ── Financial data directory — NEVER commit ───────────────────────────────────
# Covers: data/statements/, data/db/, data/exports/, data/.last_statements_dir,
#         data/.discovery_cache.json, and any other file in data/
data/

# ── SQLite database files (belt + suspenders on top of data/) ─────────────────
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# ── Generated reports & exports ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# These live in data/exports/ (covered above) but extra safety patterns:
*.xlsx
*.csv
*_report.json
*_context.json
ai_context_*.json
balance_sheet_*.json
balance_sheet_*.csv

# ── Classification memory (contains learned transaction patterns) ──────────────
classification_memory.json
*_memory.json

# ── Python virtual environment ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# ── Python cache ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python

# ── Build & distribution ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
*.egg
MANIFEST
.eggs/
wheels/
pip-wheel-metadata/

# ── Maven build output ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
webapp/target/

# ── Pytest & coverage ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
.tox/
.nox/

# ── Type checking ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.mypy_cache/
.pytype/
.pyre/
.ruff_cache/

# ── Editors & OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Jupyter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb

# ── Logs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/

# ── Temporary & scratch files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.tmp
*.temp
tmp/
temp/
scratch/
sandbox/
experiments/
dev/

# ── Profiling & benchmarks ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.prof
*.profile
profile_output/
benchmarks/results/
*.lprof

# ── Property-based testing ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.hypothesis/

# ── Development scripts — manual test scripts not meant for CI ────────────────
debug_*.py
scratch_*.py
test_manual_*.py
explore_*.py

# ── CPA corpus files — real financial figures, NEVER commit ──────────────────
# These live in statements/ but contain real Form 1065 / K-1 aggregates.
# Populated locally or from the FI_CPA_CORPUS_2024 GitHub secret.
statements/

# ── Private local config (gitignored) — institution match strings, pseudonym map ──
private/
notes/
*.draft.md

# ── Plan files (Wibey AI planning artifacts) ──────────────────────────────────
*.plan.md
.wibey/
